  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这是新疆推行“再教育营”和其他高压政策大约四年后，首府乌鲁木齐的现状、正在/曾在乌鲁木齐的民众的诉说。即便新疆最发达最繁华的地方，都一片凋零、窒息、腐败，人们纷纷逃离。前几年国内包括新疆汉族普遍力挺“再教育营”，如今被铁拳锤了几年，都受不了了。和防疫清零政策一样，这类剥夺自由损害民生换取安定的政策，都是因噎废食，一开始就错了，但非得亲身体会几年，才有所醒悟<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzhmZGM5Y2JjNDZkNTIxM2ZjMzk2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c8fdc9cbc46d5213fc396.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c8fdc9cbc46d5213fc396.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c8fdc9cbc46d5213fc396.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjgwNzZjOGEyZGViOWVmNjc0N2E1LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28076c8a2deb9ef6747a5.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28076c8a2deb9ef6747a5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/28076c8a2deb9ef6747a5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2JjMTVhZWU4Yjg0YjIxNDM0MzZhLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3bc15aee8b84b2143436a.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3bc15aee8b84b2143436a.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3bc15aee8b84b2143436a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTEwMTliM2I4ZGYzNmZiOTBkOTJhLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e1019b3b8df36fb90d92a.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e1019b3b8df36fb90d92a.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e1019b3b8df36fb90d92a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjYxNTlkMzBjMjAxN2JmYzkwNjgwLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/26159d30c2017bfc90680.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/26159d30c2017bfc90680.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/26159d30c2017bfc90680.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWNjYTZlY2ZkMzE4YTEyYzRhZTliLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cca6ecfd318a12c4ae9b.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cca6ecfd318a12c4ae9b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5cca6ecfd318a12c4ae9b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDc2YmI3MDhhOWQ1NjA1NmU4YTQwLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d76bb708a9d56056e8a40.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d76bb708a9d56056e8a40.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d76bb708a9d56056e8a40.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTc0NzYzYjhlYjZjYzVmNmY3ZGJkLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74763b8eb6cc5f6f7dbd.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74763b8eb6cc5f6f7dbd.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74763b8eb6cc5f6f7dbd.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTEzZTA5MDZhMTk5NDk5MmIwOTFiLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/113e0906a1994992b091b.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/113e0906a1994992b091b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/113e0906a1994992b091b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTgxMjRjODI4NWY3YWEyZDI3OWIxLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8124c8285f7aa2d279b1.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8124c8285f7aa2d279b1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8124c8285f7aa2d279b1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n对新疆“再教育营”政策，“新冠清零政策”就是失败的前车之鉴。“再教育营”也必然以失败收场。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n面对恐怖袭击，也只能和新冠一样“共存”。的确会死许多人，但是即便那样，也不能且也不可能通过把人都关起来解决问题。难道能把新疆各族人民都这样管制一千年吗？<br/>\n<br/>\r\n新冠和民族冲突/恐怖袭击问题，西方早给了正确答案。中国就是“不抄作业”，以民科方式、反人权甚至反人类方式对待，短期成效下代价比成效大的多，长期则是一败涂地。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n再下一个悲剧，则是气候变暖问题上中国治理失败（这个倒不是严管而是放任），死亡人数和经济民生灾难远超新冠清零和民族冲突。不信就拭目以待吧\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
